Author: sleepiestever
Text: Thanks for the insight. I hadn’t considered that but it makes sense. I have an unhealthy relationship with food but I don’t know where or if I would be categorized as having an ED.

Author: katebishophawkguy
Text: The not eating as punishment is probably rooted in control issue, especially since there seemed to be a lot of insecurity and lack of stability for you growing up.
